{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176870/extras/Wishlist.png?t=1729122592\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ragnarok is near!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ragnarok is close, monsters are invading the nine realms and have pillaged the Wizards personal collection of Artefacts, Runes and other powerful equipment! Fight your way through the nine realms to fight back against the oncoming storm, harness the power of runes and ancient magic to take back what is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Time of the Wizard\u00a0</strong>blends the thrilling elements of classic roguelikes like <i>The Binding of Isaac</i> and <i>Enter the Gungeon</i> into a unique twin-stick shooter experience. Discover endless combinations of spells and relics that alter your fate with every attempt. But beware, the creatures of the Ragnarok are fierce, and defeat means a fresh start on your path to glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you rise to reclaim the artefacts and restore balance to the realms? The fate of the gods rests in your hands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176870/extras/FeaturesPNG.png?t=1729122592\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore Unique hand-crafted rooms</strong> within procedurally generated levels. Find new enemies, items and secrets along your journey to the depths below</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Combat foes with twin-stick bullet hell action</strong> - Cast spells and exploit different enemies weaknesses to maximize your damage output.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Collect unique and fun artefacts to enhance your build.</strong> Every relic has a special effect that can completely change your run, choose wisely.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Create the spells you want to use</strong> by combining the various different elements together. They grow more powerful  along with you as you progress further into the dungeon.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176870/extras/NewGif.gif?t=1729122592\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Demo Information</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Time of the Wizard is still in it's <strong>early infancy</strong> so please be aware that bugs maybe appear and we will be working hard to fix them as fast as we possibly can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Content:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1 full level with tons of different unique rooms</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Several different cute and dangerous enemies to watch out for</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">50+ different Artefacts to collect and make interesting builds with</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An early yet challenging look at a Boss fight</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A handful of different music tracks</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">19 different creatable spells available</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A secret room to discover</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>How to play:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Time of the Wizard has the basic WASD and Mouse controls you'd expect from any game of this genre, left click to shoot and right click to dash. The main unique feature, the spell crafting wheel, is opened and closed with spacebar. TOTW also has limited controller support, again this is a very early look at what I hope to be a fun and enjoyable game so there is still many issues present. To create a spell you must open the spell wheel, with spacebar or the right stick on Xbox controller, select up to 3 elements then close it. Thank you and I hope you enjoy!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3176870?t=1729122592","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3176870?t=1729122592","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176870/65d6798322945a1fb7d9ddc0bb24f3e5f7b4d866/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729122592","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176870/65d6798322945a1fb7d9ddc0bb24f3e5f7b4d866/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729122592","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176870/extras/Wishlist.png?t=1729122592\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ragnarok is near!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ragnarok is close, monsters are invading the nine realms and have pillaged the Wizards personal collection of Artefacts, Runes and other powerful equipment! Fight your way through the nine realms to fight back against the oncoming storm, harness the power of runes and ancient magic to take back what is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Time of the Wizard\u00a0</strong>blends the thrilling elements of classic roguelikes like <i>The Binding of Isaac</i> and <i>Enter the Gungeon</i> into a unique twin-stick shooter experience. Discover endless combinations of spells and relics that alter your fate with every attempt. But beware, the creatures of the Ragnarok are fi