class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Several different cute and dangerous enemies to watch out for</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">50+ different Artefacts to collect and make interesting builds with</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An early yet challenging look at a Boss fight</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A handful of different music tracks</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">19 different creatable spells available</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A secret room to discover</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>How to play:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Time of the Wizard has the basic WASD and Mouse controls you'd expect from any game of this genre, left click to shoot and right click to dash. The main unique feature, the spell crafting wheel, is opened and closed with spacebar. TOTW also has limited controller support, again this is a very early look at what I hope to be a fun and enjoyable game so there is still many issues present. To create a spell you must open the spell wheel, with spacebar or the right stick on Xbox controller, select up to 3 elements then close it. Thank you and I hope you enjoy!</p>","developers":["Hermit Studios"],"fullgame":{"appid":"2532210","name":"Time of the Wizard"},"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176870/header.jpg?t=1729122592","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257047268,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257047268/movie480.mp4?t=1724866869","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257047268/movie_max.mp4?t=1724866869"},"name":"Time of the Wizard | Gameplay Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.a